<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2017-11-30</DATELINE><TITLE>TMPRSS2: A potential target for treatment of influenza virus and coronavirus infections</TITLE><BODY>Abstract Influenza virus and coronavirus epidemics or pandemics have occurred in succession worldwide throughout the early 21st century. These epidemics or pandemics pose a major threat to human health. Here, we outline a critical role of the host cell protease TMPRSS2 in influenza virus and coronavirus infections and highlight an antiviral therapeutic strategy targeting TMPRSS2.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>